## 🔒 Security

- **JWT** stored in HTTP-only, secure, SameSite=None cookies (for cross-origin Vercel↔Railway)
- **bcrypt** password hashing (10 salt rounds)
- **Role-based access**: Protected routes on frontend, middleware-guarded APIs on backend
- **CORS**: Whitelist of allowed origins (localhost + Vercel domains)
